Explore our menu

A simple, yet great tasting menu of all-American favorites, including freshly made burgers, crispy fries, classic sandwiches, and real ice cream, hand-spun shakes.

Burgers

All burgers are served on a brioche bun.
(V) Vegan (V) Vegeterian

The Rocket Single

Burger blastoff! A single 100% fresh, never frozen certified angus beef patty, grilled to perfection is topped with cheddar cheese, lettuce, tomato, sliced onion and our homemade Special Sauce.

The Rocket Double

Double burger blastoff! Two 100% fresh, never frozen certified angus beef patties are grilled to perfection and topped with cheddar cheese, lettuce, tomato, sliced onion and our homemade Special Sauce.

The Original

The burger that started it all. A single 1/4 lb. patty made of 100% fresh, never frozen certified angus beef, grilled to perfection and topped with lettuce, tomato, chopped onion, relish, pickles, mustard and mayo.

The Original Double

The burger that started it all. Double the 1/4 lb. patties made of 100% fresh, never frozen certified angus beef, grilled to perfection and topped with lettuce, tomato, chopped onion, relish, pickles, mustard and mayo.

The Impossible Original

The burger that started it all, except this one’s made from plants.* An Impossible patty grilled to perfection and topped with lettuce, tomato, chopped onion, relish, pickles, mustard and mayo

The Impossible Double

The burger that started it all, except this one’s made from plants. Two Impossible patties grilled to perfection and topped with lettuce, tomato, chopped onion, relish, pickles, mustard and mayo.

Bacon Cheddar

Pig out on this burger featuring crispy bacon and cheddar cheese atop a 100% fresh, never frozen certified angus beef patty, grilled to perfection. Topped with lettuce, tomato, sliced onion and our homemade Special Sauce.

Bacon Cheddar Double

Double the fun! Pig out on this burger featuring crispy bacon and cheddar cheese atop two 100% fresh, never frozen certified angus beef patties, grilled to perfection. Topped with lettuce, tomato, sliced onion and our homemade Special Sauce.

Smoke House

Rustle up your hunger for this burger featuring a single 100% fresh, never frozen certified angus beef patty, grilled to perfection and topped with bacon, cheddar cheese, crispy onion rings and our homemade Smoke House BBQ Ranch.

Smoke House Double

Rustle up your hunger for this burger featuring a two 100% fresh, never frozen certified angus beef patties, grilled to perfection and topped with bacon, cheddar cheese, crispy onion rings and our homemade Smoke House BBQ Ranch.

Spicy Houston

Smokin’ hot! This burger features a single 100% fresh, never frozen certified angus beef patty, grilled to perfection and topped with jalapenos, pepperjack cheese, lettuce, tomato and our homemade Smokin Chipotle Ranch.

Spicy Houston Double

Doubly smokin’ hot! This burger features two 100% fresh, never frozen certified angus beef patties, grilled to perfection and topped with jalapenos, pepperjack cheese, lettuce, tomato and our homemade Smokin Chipotle Ranch.

Route 66

Get your kicks with this burger featuring a single 100% fresh, never frozen certified angus beef patty, grilled to perfection and topped with swiss cheese, grilled mushrooms, caramelized onions and mayo.

Route 66 Double

Double the kicks in this burger featuring two 100% fresh, never frozen certified angus beef patties, grilled to perfection and topped with swiss cheese, grilled mushrooms, caramelized onions and mayo.

*Standard kitchen operations involve shared cooking and preparation areas where cross-contact with other foods and allergens may occur. Cross contaminants include, but are not limited to: poultry, beef, dairy, gluten, etc. Johnny Rockets is not a certified vegan restaurant.

Chicken Strips & Hot Dogs

(V) Vegan (V) Vegeterian

Chicken Strips

Crispy chicken strips seasoned and coated in a golden crunchy breading sure to delight your tastebuds.

Rocket Chili Dog

To-chili delicious! This beefy hot dog smothered in our all-meat chili, topped with diced onion and shredded cheese.

Rocket Dog

Lift off and sink your teeth into this beefy hot dog, piled high with any of the following toppings: ketchup, mustard, relish or onion.

Sandwiches

(V) Vegan (V) Vegeterian

Philly Cheese Steak

Blast off to Philly in Rockets’ version of a classic featuring thinly sliced sirloin steak topped with caramelized onions, green peppers and melty provolone cheese. Add Cheese Sauce or Mushrooms for an additional charge.

Chicken Sandwich

A juicy grilled chicken breast or crispy chicken strips topped with lettuce, tomato and mayo on a whole wheat bun.

Bacon, Lettuce & Tomato Sandwich

The all American classic sandwich features thick Applewood smoked bacon topped with lettuce, tomato and mayo on sourdough toast.

Grilled Cheese Sandwich

Say cheese to Rockets’ grilled cheese with your choice of American, cheddar, provolone, pepper jack or swiss cheese.

Chicken Club Sandwich

Join the club! A juicy grilled chicken breast is topped with bacon, lettuce, tomato and mayo on sourdough toast.

Crispy Chicken Club Sandwich

Fried for that extra crunch, this sandwich features the crispiest chicken tenders topped with bacon, lettuce, tomato and mayo on sourdough toast.

Salads

(V) Vegan (V) Vegeterian

Grilled Chicken Club Salad

The classic sandwich, salad style featuring juicy grilled chicken breast on a bed of seasonal greens, topped with crumbly bacon, diced tomatoes, shredded cheddar and your choice of dressing.

Crispy Chicken Club Salad

A crispy take on the salad style club featuring lightly breaded chicken tenders on a bed of seasonal greens, topped with crumbly bacon, diced tomatoes, shredded cheddar and your choice of dressing.

Garden Salad

Seasonal greens, diced tomatoes, shredded cheese, and choice of dressing.

Seriously Loaded Sides

(V) Vegan (V) Vegeterian

Fries

Skin-on and fried extra crispy, they’re our burgers’ favorite side. Order your way with hearty all-meat chili, cheese or bacon!

Tots

Grated and deep fried, these tots are tot-ally crispy on the outside with tender insides. Order your way with hearty all-meat chili, cheese or bacon!

Onion Rings

Jumbo sized onion rings are rolled in crunchy sourdough breadcrumbs, fried to golden brown perfection.

Chili Bowl

Enjoy our hearty all-meat chili by the bowlful, sprinkled with cheddar cheese and diced onions.

Beverages

(V) Vegan (V) Vegeterian

Sodas & More

Get your refreshments here! From fizzy sodas to iced tea, Rockets knows how to quench your thirst.

Kid’s Meal

For rocketeers ages 12 and under. Includes a kid's sized entrée, fries, and a drink. Upgrade any kids-sized drink to a kids-sized Original or Deluxe Shake for an extra charge. Any add-ons or additional toppings are an additional charge. Kid's Meals are available at participating Johnny Rockets locations.
(V) Vegan (V) Vegeterian

Kids Mini Burger

Two mini burgers made of 100% fresh, never frozen certified angus beef patties, grilled to perfection and topped with choice of ketchup, mustard or pickles.

Kids Chicken Strips

Perfect for dipping, our lightly breaded chicken tenders are served with your choice of dipping sauce.

Kids Hot Dog

Ready for launch, this beefy dog is topped with their choice of ketchup, mustard, relish or onion.

Kids Grilled Chicken Strips

Fired up on the grill, these grilled juicy chicken strips are served with their choice of dipping sauce.

Kids Grilled Cheese

Say cheese! Offered with your choice of American, cheddar, provolone, pepper jack or swiss cheese.

Kids Original Shakes

Sweet and satisfying to launch kiddos into orbit, their choice between Hershey’s chocolate, very strawberry and sweet vanilla flavors.

Kids Deluxe Shakes

Upgrade that sweetness to the moon!Their choice of Oreo Cookie Chocolate Swirl, Oreo Cookies and Cream, Strawberry Oreo Crumble, Peanut Butter, Peanut Butter Banana, Hershey’s Chocolate Peanut Butter, Hershey’s Chocolate Banana, Hershey’s Chocolate Strawberry Kiss, Strawberry Banana and Banana flavors.

Shakes

(V) Vegan (V) Vegeterian

Hershey’s ® Chocolate Shake

A spun sweet shake made with real vanilla ice cream and Hershey’s chocolate syrup.

Strawberry Shake

A spun sweet shake made with real ice cream and strawberries.

Vanilla Shake

A spun sweet shake made with real vanilla ice cream.

Oreo ® Cookies & Cream Shake

A Johnny Rockets favorite – the classic delight of our Oreo® Cookies & Cream Shake. Real vanilla ice cream blended with chunks of Oreo® cookies, creating a rich and satisfying shake that’s a perfect marriage of creaminess and crunch.

Oreo ® Strawberry Crumble Shake

A playful twist on a classic! Our Oreo® Strawberry Crumble Shake features the unbeatable combination of strawberries and Oreo® cookie crumbles, mixed to perfection for a sweet, fruity, and delicious shake.

Hershey’s ® Chocolate Banana Shake

Dive into a world of chocolatey bliss with our Hershey’s® Chocolate Banana Shake. Creamy Hershey’s® chocolate meets the natural sweetness of bananas, creating a shake that’s a match made in dessert heaven.

Hershey’s ® Chocolate Peanut Butter Shake

Satisfy your cravings with our Hershey’s® Chocolate Peanut Butter Shake. Hershey’s® chocolate meets the creamy richness of peanut butter, resulting in a decadent shake that’s a harmonious blend of sweet and nutty.

Hershey’s ® Chocolate Strawberry Shake

Experience the perfect fusion of flavors with our Hershey’s® Chocolate Strawberry Shake. Hershey’s® chocolate and strawberries come together in a delightful shake that’s both refreshing and delicious.

Chocolate Chip Cookie Shake

Treat yourself to the nostalgia of freshly baked cookies in a glass. Our Chocolate Chip Cookie Shake combines the classic taste of freshly-baked chocolate chip cookies with real vanilla ice cream, delivering a shake that feels like a warm hug for your taste buds.

Strawberry Banana Shake

A fruity sensation awaits in our Strawberry Banana Shake. Strawberries and banana blend seamlessly with real vanilla ice cream for a refreshing and wholesome shake that’s perfect for any occasion.

Peanut Butter Banana Shake

Enjoy the perfect marriage of nutty and fruity with our Peanut Butter Banana Shake. Smooth peanut butter meets bananas in a creamy concoction that’s both satisfying and delicious.

Peanut Butter Shake

For the peanut butter enthusiasts, our Peanut Butter Shake is a dream come true. Rich and creamy peanut butter blended with real vanilla ice cream creates a shake that’s nutty, velvety, and utterly irresistible.

Banana Shake

Keep it simple and delightful with our Banana Shake. Sweet bananas blended to perfection with creamy, real vanilla ice cream, offering a smooth and timeless treat that’s both comforting and delicious.

Craig’s Vegan Vanilla Shake

The classic made vegan using Craig’s cashew based ice cream, oat milk, and coconut milk whipped cream. This product contains nuts. Standard kitchen operations involve shared cooking and preparation areas where cross-contact with other foods and allergens may occur. Johnny Rockets is not a certified vegan restaurant.

Craig’s Vegan Strawberry Shake

The classic made vegan using Craig’s cashew based ice cream, oat milk, and coconut milk whipped cream. This product contains nuts. Standard kitchen operations involve shared cooking and preparation areas where cross-contact with other foods and allergens may occur. Johnny Rockets is not a certified vegan restaurant.

Craig’s Vegan Chocolate Shake

The classic made vegan using Craig’s cashew based ice cream, oat milk, and coconut milk whipped cream. This product contains nuts. Standard kitchen operations involve shared cooking and preparation areas where cross-contact with other foods and allergens may occur. Johnny Rockets is not a certified vegan restaurant.
